PrecisAmendments to the MANITOBA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1987 which close portions of the Winnipeg and Nelson Rivers to fishing for lake sturgeon and allow the province to close any waters to fishing for a particular species and to vary any such closure as the need arises.
